703942f-a.title: Brooklyn: Debevoise Avenue - Division Place
703942f-a.text:
Debevoise Ave., west side, between Division Place and Richardson Street. O1d Woodpoint Road, went southward on ground occupied by these
homes.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
